\c 4
\s Kuidzwa kwaJesu
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jesu wakatungamirirwa neMweya kurenje kuti anoidzwa nadhiabhorosi.
\v 2 Zvino wakati atsanya mazuva makumi mana neusiku makumi mana, akazonzwa nzara.
\v 3 Zvino muidzi wakati auya kwaari, akati: Kana uri Mwanakomana waMwari, raira kuti mabwe awa aite zvingwa.
\v 4 Asi wakapindura akati: Kwakanyorwa \add kuchinzi\add*: Munhu haangararami nechingwa choga, asi neshoko rimwe nerimwe rinobuda mumuromo maMwari.
\p
\v 5 Zvino dhiabhorosi akamutora akamuisa muguta dzvene, akamumisa pachiruvu chetembere,
\v 6 ndokuti kwaari: Kana uri Mwanakomana waMwari, zvikandire pasi; nekuti kwakanyorwa kuti: Iye ucharaira vatumwa vake pamusoro pako, pamaoko vachakugamha, zvimwe ungagumbusa rutsoka rwako pabwe.
\v 7 Jesu akati kwaari: Kwakanyorwa zvekare: Usaidza Ishe Mwari wako.
\p
\v 8 Dhiabhorosi akamuisazve pagomo refusa, akamuratidza ushe hwose hwenyika, nekubwinya kwahwo.
\v 9 Akati kwaari: Zvose zvinhu izvi ndichapa kwauri kana ukawira pasi ukandinamata.
\v 10 Ipapo Jesu akati kwaari: Ibva, Satani, nekuti kwakanyorwa \add kuchinzi\add*: Uchanamata Ishe Mwari wako, uchashumira iye woga.
\v 11 Ipapo dhiabhorosi akamusiya; zvino tarira, vatumwa vakauya vakamushandira.
\s Jesu unotanga basa paGarirea
\p
\v 12 Zvino Jesu wakati anzwa kuti Johwani wakumikidzwa \add mutirongo\add*, akabva akaenda Garirea.
\v 13 Zvino wakabva Nazareta, akasvika akandogara muKapenaumi riri pagungwa, pamiganhu yeZebhuroni neNafitarimi;
\v 14 kuti zvizadzisike zvakarehwa naIsaya muporofita, achiti:
\v 15 Nyika yeZebhuroni nenyika yeNefitarimi, \add pa\add*nzira yegungwa, mhiri kwaJoridhani, Garirea revahedheni;
\v 16 vanhu vakange vagere murima vakaona chiedza chikuru; nevakange vagere panharaunda nemumumvuri werufu, chiedza chakabudira kwavari.
\s Jesu anotanga kuparidza
\p
\v 17 Kubvira panguva iyoyo Jesu wakatanga kuparidza nekuti: Tendeukai, nekuti ushe hwekumatenga hwaswedera.
\s Kudamwa kwevadzidzi vekutanga
\p
\v 18 Zvino Jesu wakati achifamba-famba pagungwa reGarirea akaona vana vemunhu umwe vaviri, Simoni anonzi Petro, naAndiriya munun'una wake, vachikandira mumbure mugungwa; nekuti vakange vari varedzi.
\v 19 Akati kwavari: Nditeverei, ndigokuitai varedzi vevanhu.
\v 20 Pakarepo vakasiya mimbure vakamutevera.
\v 21 Zvino wakati apfuurira kubva ipapo akaona vamwe vaviri vanakomana vemunhu umwe, Jakobho waZebhedhi naJohwani munun'una wake muchikepe pamwe naZebhedhi baba vavo, vachigadzira mimbure yavo, akavadana.
\v 22 Pakarepo vakasiya chikepe nababa vavo vakamutevera.
\s Jesu anobata munyika yeGarirea
\p
\v 23 Jesu akapota neGarirea rose achidzidzisa mumasinagoge avo, nekuparidza evhangeri yeushe, achiporesa ukosha hwose neurwere hwose pevanhu.
\v 24 Shoko rake rikabudira kuSiria yose; vakauyisa kwaari varwere vose, vakabatwa nehosha dzakasiyana siyana nemarwadzo, nevakange vane madhimoni, nevaiva nezvipusha, nevakange vakafa mitezo; akavaporesa.
\v 25 Zvino zvaunga zvikuru zvakamutevera, vaibva Garirea, neDhekapori, neJerusarema, neJudhiya, nemhiri kwaJoridhani.
